name: 'threesixtyfive' Zip-Up Hoodie Men's (Navy)
description:
Introducing our 'threesixtyfive' Men's Hoodie from Pimp Factory! Get your pimp on year round in our final release of 2013. Featuring a massive 3-color print on the back and a 3-color print across the zipper on the front.

These are preshrunk, but if you dry them on high they will still shrink some. If you like a baggier hoodie, I would recommend ordering a size up, most people last year tended to bump up a size.

We are printing these using a different screen-printing method using a water-based ink. They do not have that heavy feel of a normal screenprinted garment, It basically dyes the image into the fabric.

Printed on Gildan, Heavy Blend, blanks.
- 8 oz., 50% cotton/50% polyester preshrunk fleece full zip hooded sweatshirt.
- Unlined hood with matching drawstring.
- Front pouch pockets.
- 1x1 athletic rib knit cuffs and waistband with spandex.
- Set-in sleeves
- Double-needle stitched throughout

description:

These are preshrunk, but if you dry them on high they will still shrink some.

We are printing these using a different screen-printing method using a water-based ink. This means two things to you. 1) They do not have that heavy feel of a normal screenprinted garment, It basically dyes the image into the fabric so its a really cool feature. 2) Your hoodie print will feel a little stiff until after the first wash. This is completely normal and it achieves the desired finished product.
